--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 1.1.2 (2020-10-30)
E: Simplify Ansible file header (ansible_managed)

* Version 1.1.1 (2020-10-30)
E: Simplify checksum verification

* Version 1.1.0 (2020-06-29)
C: Update 'node_exporter' to version '1.0.1'

* Version 1.0.0 (2020-06-29)
C: Redesign role to support SELinux

* Version 0.6.1 (2020-05-27)
B: Remove 'creates' Ansible parameter (make unarchive override files)

* Version 0.6.0 (2020-05-27)
F: Update 'node_exporter' to version '1.0.0'

* Version 0.5.0 (2019-11-13)
C: Add support for Debian 10
C: Drop support for Debian 9

* Version 0.4.0 (2019-06-12)
F: Update 'node_exporter' to version '0.18.1'

* Version 0.3.0 (2019-05-26)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.8

* Version 0.2.0 (2019-05-10)
F: Update 'node_exporter' to version '0.18.0'

* Version 0.1.1 (2019-01-07)
E: Change POSIX permissions for 'textfile_collector' directory

* Version 0.1.0 (2019-01-02)
F: Initial release
